{"tid":1238493,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例 與 廿三條 的關係","createTime":"2019-06-18T00:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T06:08:59.000Z","uid":144731,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"54320d36c4d867fea4137069e5a129a7960c4a20","tid":1238493,"uid":144731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:06:10.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人講過/諗過<br />\n<br />\n送中條例其中一個規則係唔會一罪兩審<br />\n<br />\n（<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/panels/se/papers/se20190531cb2-1578-1-c.pdf&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjsiPmN2_HiAhXLE4gKHcUACM8QFjABegQIAxAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw3rVU0IQcjc2zWIKVd3jtky\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fse%2Fpapers%2Fse20190531cb2-1578-1-c.pdf%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjsiPmN2_HiAhXLE4gKHcUACM8QFjABegQIAxAB%26usg%3DAOvVaw3rVU0IQcjc2zWIKVd3jtky&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=cd467099\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/panels/se/papers/se20190531cb2-1578-1-c.pdf&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjsiPmN2_HiAhXLE4gKHcUACM8QFjABegQIAxAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw3rVU0IQcjc2zWIKVd3jtky</a>）re: 附件一 (b)<br />\n<br />\n其實個目的就係想香港就廿三條立法<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例若果成功修訂後，假如中共話要拉你告你危害國家安全，就一定會送你中返去受審，但相信無香港人會想喺大陸受審<br />\n<br />\n因此，政府就會話為咗避免港人送中，基於唔會一罪兩審原則，就唯有喺香港立法廿三條<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以為逃犯條例立法根本就係為廿三條鋪路！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"121b2eea49a1a38cafde01a1ead06c63901fd63f","tid":1238493,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:07:41.000Z","msg":"佢話唔引度政治犯喎"},{"pid":"c5cf859278f0f11addd2f9f0d70d5907e687c68f","tid":1238493,"uid":144731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"121b2eea49a1a38cafde01a1ead06c63901fd63f","tid":1238493,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:07:41.000Z","msg":"佢話唔引度政治犯喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:16:15.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力算唔算政治犯？<br />\n話你組織邪教又算唔算？<br />\n竊取國家機密又點計數？<br />\n<br />\n廿三條太廣闊"},{"pid":"b8d1d75338dbb1ea6c7700d2284a0e9a8d5f010c","tid":1238493,"uid":39693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"121b2eea49a1a38cafde01a1ead06c63901fd63f","tid":1238493,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:07:41.000Z","msg":"佢話唔引度政治犯喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:29:58.000Z","msg":"艾未未果啲都唔係政治罪架<br />\n<br />\n要搵個罪入你有幾難，到時真係立咗就仲死<br />\n<br />\n釋法佢話事 任佢up"},{"pid":"117c470a9bcd8120a37f1ccf9ea4493c031f8227","tid":1238493,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:37:29.000Z","msg":"如果你講既野係成立既，就有白臉叫立23條。事實係2條都係仆街。<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"9408febe919072f29fbb583cd90e65c5efb83439","tid":1238493,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117c470a9bcd8120a37f1ccf9ea4493c031f8227","tid":1238493,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:37:29.000Z","msg":"如果你講既野係成立既，就有白臉叫立23條。事實係2條都係仆街。<ins></ins>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:39:16.000Z","msg":"之前咪有"},{"pid":"5b9af2c25c712c320bdf99239f701b38c826ab4f","tid":1238493,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121b2eea49a1a38cafde01a1ead06c63901fd63f","tid":1238493,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:07:41.000Z","msg":"佢話唔引度政治犯喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vwoS9O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vwoS9O.png&h=d2d4819b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46e9dd2a704b873218bd0a43038c7aea14d9050c","tid":1238493,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:43:08.000Z","msg":"講真 今次俾佢過左逃犯<br />\n等於開左大門俾中共<br />\n到時就會有第二次修例 第三次 第四次<br />\n到時就唔只廿三條<br />\n可能仲有啲仲惡既惡法<br />\n所以真係唔可以俾呢條過<br />\n逃犯只係為香港同中共接軌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人一定要頂住啊</span>"},{"pid":"9989712d79e571891b9bee8defe92546ff2f0e23","tid":1238493,"uid":144731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a1ff407956d6d3d7dfad4d5da68d4ba12102dbc","tid":1238493,"uid":68541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}